(8, 8, 'ws 8.pdf', 'ws_page_08.jpg', 'LAWRENCE ANTHONY  A tribute to the late Lawrence Anthony, internationally respected conservationist and The cause advert to raise awareness of rhino poaching designed by Roots advertising and branding agency highlights the core of the issue - demand. It has been published in English and Mandarin, and is available for download for the viral campaign to show how environmental crime is hurting South Africans.MIDNIGHT WITH AN ANTI-  POACHING TEAMPeople often ask - why cant the poaching just be stopped? This article gives one insight into how difficult it is to patrol, monitor, and manage vast, vast tracts of land. DR IAN PLAYER SPEAKS OUTDr Ian Player is recognised for being key to saving the white rhino from extinction. No one would have thought that all these years later he would be giving his views to save this magnificent animal from the brink of extinction once again. Wildside interviewed him on his views and the history he gives in itself provides answers.Vincent Christoforous, CEO of King Shaka Aviation and Dr Bandile Mkhize, CEO of Ezemvelo KZN Wildlife  Page 24BOOK GIVEAWAYWIN A SHARK CAVE DIVEKirsten Dukes, South Africas Miss Earth ambassador helps protect endangered species  Page 42'),
(9, 9, 'ws 9.pdf', 'ws_page_09.jpg', 'Its been said that in any warfare aerial support is necessary and when it comes to the war on poaching aerial support has proven to be effective. Read about this successful project that must continue.HUNTING PERMITS IN THE SPOTLIGHTBogus or pseudo hunting is a situation where legal hunting permits have been abused. Recent comments from government at the time of going to press encouragingly said that they were focusing on this. YOGA BUSH BREAKWhat could possibly be more relaxing than enjoying yoga outdoors? If you agree, then be sure to book your place soonest because places are limited.KOSI BAY MISS EARTH AT WOODLANDSMiss Earth raises the profile of endangered species and visited Wooldands Lodge.If you have a cool R115 000 and a full month of free time then you are in the game to experience Africas most comprehensive shark diving adventure experienceKnowledge can help you prevent a shark attack  Page 63ILDSIDErugby player, becomes a Wildside Warrior - pg 17'),
