(48, 48, 'ws 48.pdf', 'ws_page_48.jpg', 'ANCHORS RESTIN THE HEART OF UMHLANGAA sparkling pool, tropical gardens, warm ambience and excellent accommo-dation awaits you at Anchors Rest 4 star Guest House, located in the heart of Umhlanga Rocks.  From here it is an easy walk to the beautiful swimming beaches, numerous shops, boutiques, restaurants, coffee bars, and vibrant night life. Anchors Rest has affordable, luxury accommodation for the busi-ness or leisure travellers with large, well-appointed rooms all with private entrance and patio with BBQ facilities.  All rooms are air conditioned and feature DSTV,  Free Wi-, hospitality tray and safes and own lounge area. Delicious full English style or continental breakfasts are served. Come and enjoy this wonderful Guest House with a full suite of facilities which also include a solar heated swimming pool and secure off street parking for guest vehicles. Anchors Rest is close to Gateway Theatre of Shopping, King Shaka International Airport, Sibaya Casino, many top quality golf courses, numerous tourist attractions and business parks. Credit cards accepted and children over 10 years welcome.  031 561 7380  (fax) 031 561 6249  (cell)  083 631 9344     enquiries@anchorsrest.co.za   www.anchorsrest.co.za '),
