(37, 'No', 'No', 'Competitions', 0, '', 'Win a two night stay for two at Fordoun Boutique Hotel and Spa', 'fordounpool.jpg', '', '', 'Fordoun Boutique Hotel and Spa in the KwaZulu-Midlands provides the perfect escape. \r\nSet in tranquil surroundings with a magnificent spa it is a real haven of relaxation. They are fast gaining a reputation for exquisite food too.', 'A lucky Wildside reader can win two nights’ accommodation including breakfast for two people sharing, midweek in a Superior Mountain View Room. The prize is valid until January 2013.', 'Enter the competition', '', '2012-10-01 09:03:00', '2012-10-01 09:03:00', '<span style="color:red;">Question: What is the name of the famous tourism area that&nbsp;Fordoun Boutique Hotel and Spa is found?</span>', ''),
