(54, 'yes', 'yes', 'Competitions', 1, '', 'WIN A WILDSIDE SPA PRIZE VALUED AT R8000', 'spa_comp_dec.jpg', '', '', 'Win a two night stay in a superior room at the Valley Lodge & Spa in the historical Magaliesberg, including breakfast, lunch and dinner, valued at R8,000.', 'Your prize includes a glorious spa Best Friends package, comprising a 5 hour spa treatment for two, valued at R1350 per person, including:energising body wrap and exfoliation, 45 minute back, neck and shoulder massage, hydrotherapy, reflexology treatment and a light spa lunch with a bottle of Cap Classique - don’t forget to take bathing costumes for the private spa hydro facilities.', '', '', '2013-12-17 17:28:00', '2013-12-17 17:29:00', 'Question: What is the area name that Valley Lodge & Spa is situated in?', '');
